videos.headline: Mond pushes in TD for Texas A&M
videos.description: Kellen Mond keeps the ball himself and gets in for a short touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mond pushes in TD for Texas A&M) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Mond runs in another TD
videos.description: Kellen Mond fakes the handoff and takes the ball in himself for a 12-yard touchdown to pad Texas A&M's lead.

videos.headline: Shrader, Guidry connect for 32-yard TD
videos.description: Garrett Shrader airs it out to Stephen Guidry for a 32-yard Mississippi State touchdown.

videos.headline: Mond throws to an open Ausbon to pad Texas A&M's lead
videos.description: Jhamon Ausbon gets open and hauls in Kellen Mond's pass for a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mond throws to an open Ausbon to pad Texas A&M's lead) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Rodgers shows off incredible determination on TD
videos.description: Kendrick Rodgers catches the ball and appears to be taken down by multiple defenders, but he rolls and keeps himself up to get into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rodgers shows off incredible determination on TD) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Wydermyer breaks several tackles for 52-yard TD
videos.description: Jalen Wydermyer makes the catch and eludes multiple Mississippi State defenders for a 52-yard Texas A&M touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wydermyer breaks several tackles for 52-yard TD) 2019/10/26
